OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe Budget will provide an extra #100
OL,8,Fmillion for public spending in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland in 2024-25, the
OL,10,FGovernment has said.JChancellor Jeremy
OL,11,FHunt has also announced regeneration
OL,12,Ffunds of #20 million each for
OL,13,FLondonderry and Coleraine over 10
OL,14,Fyears.JThe Government has also
OL,15,Fallocated #2 million to be spent on
OL,16,Fglobal investment and trade
OL,17,Fopportunities for Northern Ireland.
