OL,7,FHowever, Stormont leaders have been
OL,8,Fcritical of the demand.JNorthern
OL,9,FIreland Office minister Steve Baker
OL,10,Fsaid: "We do expect revenue raising.
OL,11,F"For far too long both public service
OL,12,Freform and revenue raising have been
OL,13,Fneglected in Northern Ireland.J"We
OL,14,Fwill obviously work through the
OL,15,Fdetails in collaboration with the
OL,16,FExecutive.J"But as a Government we are
OL,17,Fvery clear that revenue raising is
OL,18,Fintertwined with what we've said about
OL,19,Fdebt write-off.J"I want to be
OL,20,Fabsolutely clear with the public and
OL,21,Fthe Executive that Northern Ireland
OL,22,Fneeds to be put on a sustainable
OL,23,Ffinancial footing and we need to have
OL,24,Fpublic service reform."
